provisions.content:
In this Ordinance, unless there is anything repugnant in the
subject or context.-
(a)      "Academy" means the Health Services Academy;
(b)      "Board" means the Board of Governors of the Academy;
(c)     "Committee" means the Executive Committee of the
Academy;
(d)     "Council" means the Academic Advisory Council of the
Academy;
(e)     "Executive Director" means the Executive Director of the
Academy;
(f)      "rules" and "regulations" mean the rules and regulations made
under this Ordinance; and
(g)     "Teacher" includes Head of Department, Professors, Associate
professors, Assistant Professors, Lecturers, Instructors and
Research Staff engaged by the Academy, or such other persons
as may be recognised to be teachers by the Committee.
